This paper deals with wireless communication networks and their throughput, which are topics that fall under the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the effects of fading, which is a topic related to Multimedia (cs.MM) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-categories.
